messages.content:
Here are the payload-wrapped calls for each step in the process.

### 1. Create Skill
```json
{
  "action": "create_skill",
  "payload": {
    "title": "Unit Testing with Pytest",
    "type": "skill",
    "scope": "global",
    "description": "Write unit tests using pytest framework",
    "skill_level": "intermediate",
    "triggers": [
      "test",
      "pytest"
    ],
    "aliases": [
      "pytest-testing",
      "python-testing-guide"
    ],
    "required_tools": [
      "pytest"
    ]
  }
}
```

### 2. Search for Alias
```json
{
  "action": "search_skill",
  "payload": {
    "query": "pytest-testing"
  }
}
```

### 3. Verification
```json
{
  "action": "verify_result",
  "payload": {
    "searched_alias": "pytest-testing",
    "expected_title": "Unit Testing with Pytest",
    "match_criteria": "aliases contains searched_alias"
  }
}
```

